parameters:
Lucia: Luuna, you're too late. The Holy Grail has been moved to
another location.

Lucia: There's no chance of victory for you anymore. Give up and
behave yourselves.

Lucia: A final piece of advice. The generals of Valentina are not the
kind you can reason with.

Lucia: If you continue to interfere with us, there's no telling what
they'll do.

Lucia: You have defeated Valentina's sorcerers. Therefore, I cannot
stop you. If you withdraw now, I will report it to Sylvia.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I won't be intimidated by such threats.

Lucia: Even if you use the Holy Grail, which is said to contain Regnus
Grahardt's magical power, you cannot defeat us. Either way.
Lucia: You have no need to know that.

Lucia: Luuna, I've warned you. If you won't give up, whatever happens
is not my concern.
Becky: Sigh... It's a shame. We didn't get the Holy Grail.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] There must be another way. Let's return to Norva-Na for now.
